<profile version="1.4">
  <notes>For the game Conquer Online (Conquer.exe)
-------------------------------------------------------
Freely available from: co.91.com

This profile has a mode called "Active". When you are in Active mode, Alt Controller will repeatedly press F6 for you whenever the mouse is in a small region in the centre of the screen (for casting potions). It will stop pressing F6 when you move the mouse out of the region again.

To enable the "Active" mode, press Z.
To return to the "Default" mode, press X. 

Thanks to www.gamebase.info user @Alex for creating the the original version of this profile!</notes>
